Business Brief -- USA Waste Services Inc.:
   Purchases of Firms, Landfill
   Set for Total $15.3 Million
The company said it funded the transactions with four
different sellers by expanding its bank credit line and
selling shares in a small private placement, and through the
exercise of warrants. USA Waste currently has about nine
million shares outstanding.
   USA Waste said the purchases should add about $14 million
to its 1992 revenue. It had 1991 revenue of about $19
million.